Goal:
- Kill the final boss at the end of the dungeon 


Objects:

Characters:
- 1 protagonist
- 3 side characters 
- Enemies 
- 1 boss enemy 
- 1 sub boss enemy 

Shops: (in town)
- weapon + armor shop
- item shop
- crafting shop (crafting weapons and armor with resources collected after battles)
- item crafting shop (resources obtained after battles)

Dungeon:
- can go to the dungeon from the town
- has some amount of floors
- will spawn a random amount of enemy groups
- defeating all enemy groups on a floor you can advance to the next floor

options:

- user should be able to save progress
